          reached:job_duo
          see:the heist landed straight into the collection — every file byte-faithful to its source hash on the disk
          see:the landing filed by category — each track under the genre its filing named
          see:a mislabeled file followed its tags home — the filing trusted the bytes over the filename
          see:the landing streamed chunk by chunk — no whole track ever waited in memory
