          reached:job_reuno
          see:the mirror heist landed the other way — each end filed the same disk under its own categories
          offered:reuno,n=9
          manifest:reuno,holds=9
          heisted:reuno,skipped=9,held_named=9
          see:a second heist found nothing new — the catalog identity of every offer was already held
          reached:logs
          newlyadded_shape,uno=3,duo=6,unsourced
          see:newlyadded logs each arrival with a fresh feeling — and never a word about the source
          reached:deny
          denied,drop_artist:Fourier Four,drop_title:Echo E,gone,carded_off,log_dropped
          see:a denied track left the collection — the file gone and the log honest about the drop
          reached:job_retomb
          offered:retomb,n=9
          manifest:retomb,holds=8,refuses
          see:the manifest named every verdict before a byte moved — the heist showed what it would take hold and refuse
          heisted:retomb,skipped=8,tombstoned
          see:a denied track stayed refused on the next heist — the collection remembered the rejection and re-downloaded nothing
          see:every offer left a named verdict on the job — took held or denied each pointed by tune
          reached:flat
          flattened
          see:the scaffolding flattened away — no heist stands and nothing attributes who gave what
